Others (including non-profit organizations) with credit available elsewhere

7.125



For Economic Injury:



Businesses and small agricultural cooperatives without credit available elsewhere

4.000


</TABLE>


The number assigned to this disaster for physical damage is 272806 and for economic injury the number is 829300.




(Catalog of Federal Domestic Assistance Program Nos. 59002 and 59008).




Dated: July 14, 1994.



